title: Aaron Rodgers’s Last Dance, Rookie Watch, and Mailbag
description:
Nora Princiotti and Mallory Rubin kick off the show by taking a deeper look into Aaron Rodgers and his relationship with the Packers and how that will affect their season (5:58). Then they discuss rookies they’re looking forward to watching this week (38:20), and they end the episode answering a couple mailbag questions (51:00).

Hosts: Nora Princiotti and Mallory Rubin
Production Assistant: Isaiah Blakely
Additional Production Supervision: Arjuna Ramgopal
